{"tid":2221215,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾馬利執教生涯里程「悲」 領6隊作客魯營13戰全敗","createTime":"2020-09-28T08:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T08:12:46.000Z","uid":39912,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be26b2166edb19a0a6820ecae850a536e754bbfc","tid":2221215,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:07:54.000Z","msg":"2004年底於洛卡（Lorca Deportiva）展開教練生涯的艾馬利，周日領維拉利爾在西甲往訪巴塞隆拿，是其執教生涯的第800場比賽。然而，這名48歲西班牙籍主帥卻遭遇里程「悲」，球隊以0:4慘敗予巴塞，他分別領六支球隊作客魯營鬥巴塞，連續13仗都輸波收場。<br />\n<br />\n艾馬利首次領軍作客在魯營受挫巴塞隆拿是於2007/08球季，當時他帶領艾美利亞作客以0:2不敵由列卡特任主帥的巴塞。<br />\n<br />\n作為華倫西亞教練期間，艾馬利於西甲領軍作客曾被巴塞以4:0、3:1、2:1及5:1打敗，亦曾於西班牙盃4強作客以0:2不敵巴塞。<br />\n<br />\n其後，艾馬利出任莫斯科斯巴達教練，球隊於歐聯分組賽作客魯營被巴塞以3:2打擊敗，而他之後任教西維爾，四度作客巴塞亦以1:2、2:3、1:5和1:2落敗。<br />\n<br />\n艾馬利執教法甲巴黎日耳門（PSG）期間，曾於2017年的歐聯16強與巴塞對壘，惟球隊首回合大勝4:0後，次回合卻被遭回到主場魯營的巴塞大炒6:1而出局。周日一役，艾馬利領第六支球隊第13次作客魯營，但宿命難違，仍然難逃一敗。"},{"pid":"bceb9762b976d6490bb1ebafddeccab824af819a","tid":2221215,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:08:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200928/QB45NO74TNHMVND2KMUGZXFDAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200928%2FQB45NO74TNHMVND2KMUGZXFDAE%2F&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIe4Wvb5rKEvwepesSl%2FR16E%3D&h=e480cd32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20200928%2FQB45NO74TNHMVND2KMUGZXFDAE%2F&h=0f20a889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20200928/QB45NO74TNHMVND2KMUGZXFDAE/</a>"},{"pid":"44fde1cbd1de3337b7af1496da8c73a256fc566f","tid":2221215,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:09:28.000Z","msg":"愛狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa09c7a6aad215e5a36f4d510649ffd59ede7a1","tid":2221215,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:09:33.000Z","msg":"心理一定有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa37b4567c3cb782d39335a50c427a54a83e17ef","tid":2221215,"uid":10008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"好彩果時有阿唔駛對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e350cd0f39f007ceca24e4b8423cd928f0843f6a","tid":2221215,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa37b4567c3cb782d39335a50c427a54a83e17ef","tid":2221215,"uid":10008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:11:33.000Z","msg":"好彩果時有阿唔駛對<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"上季甘伯盃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}